title: #92Noon! Parise/Snob/Guerin/Boudreau/BA
description: Hear from Zach Parise to open the show, followed by Stump the Snob to end the first hour. Then Bill Guerin and Bruce Boudreau are back-to-back midway thru. Brian Arrigoni in studio the final stretch to chat about hockey, horses and the NICU.
